               <p>ARTHUR WILCOXON. I am a <rs id="t18280529-252-viclabel1391" type="occupation">looking-glass manufacturer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-252-victim1360 t18280529-252-viclabel1391"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18280529-252-crimeloc1392">Lombard-street</placeName>
